cms.query.QueryText: SELECT MetaFileID, MetaFileObjectID, MetaFileObjectType, MetaFileGroupName, MetaFileName, MetaFileExtension, MetaFileSize, MetaFileMimeType, MetaFileImageWidth, MetaFileImageHeight, MetaFileGUID, MetaFileLastModified, [MetaFileTitle], [MetaFileDescription], [MetaFileCustomData] FROM CMS_MetaFile WHERE [MetaFileGUID] = @Guid
